reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars DO NOT BUY FOR GAMING
reviews.reviewText: Let me start by saying that a 40$ phone from Walmart has more processing power than this thing. Don't believe me? Well I tested it. I downloaded Fallout Shelter through steam for this laptop and it stuttered so much I'm pretty sure it was running tourettes.exe. For those who don't know Fallout Shelter is a MOBILE APP and almost ANYTHING else in the world can run it except this laptop. This laptop is NOT for gaming at all. It can not run ANY game at all and you should absolutely save your money. Not to mention that the RBG backlights for the keyboard are so light that you can't see them unless it's pitch black and your face is shoved directly into the keyboard. I have never returned a product so fact but this is easily the worst computer I have ever purchased. It has NO processing power, It can't even run games meant for cheap mobile phones, I wouldn't even recommend it for office use. The fact this laptop is 400$ is one of the biggest scams I have ever seen as it's not worth more than 35$ (note how I priced it less than the 40$ phone I used to to compare speeds to)
